      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who wants basic transport, a project, or a handy backup vehicle. A great chance to get into a car without spending big money, and priced to reflect its condition. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
